":58604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:09:50.000Z","msg":"其實點定義為難唱先？<br />\n計音準嘅話<br />\n係咪代表好多人唔識唱歌？<br />\n定係佢地覺得難唱到eason咁有感情"},{"pid":"647da4031edf69c967006066405276d1cffc55b4","tid":285272,"uid":3852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:17:42.000Z","msg":"富士山下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最難唱之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08f65ba37888a3429360e4c51126a92748f0564","tid":285272,"uid":62551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點定義為難唱先？<br />\n計音準嘅話<br />\n係咪代表好多人唔識唱歌？<br />\n定係佢地覺得難唱到eason咁有感情</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多巴打都話唱到eason既歌 但唱唔出佢既感情 或者咁形容： <br />\n 當你地指既感情 就係佢既音域 隻歌音域闊，而你無咁闊既音域 唱就變左唔岩feel/唔好聽，其實係因為音域窄先會有咁既錯覺"},{"pid":"873bc8c2c83680acd2f18a9e7abf9e6da05941ee","tid":285272,"uid":3852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實點定義為難唱先？<br />\n計音準嘅話<br />\n係咪代表好多人唔識唱歌？<br />\n定係佢地覺得難唱到eason咁有感情</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多巴打都話唱到eason既歌 但唱唔出佢既感情 或者咁形容： <br />\n 當你地指既感情 就係佢既音域 隻歌音域闊，而你無咁闊既音域 唱就變左唔岩feel/唔好聽，其實係因為音域窄先會有咁既錯覺</blockquote><br />\n仲有天生把聲呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小朋友音域都夠闊 把聲唔夠mature/唔夠磁性/timbre唔夠好 都唱唔出eason個feel"},{"pid":"0f3421d30d08d90257dc5d242e61792abc6de1eb","tid":285272,"uid":75426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如不見<br />\n好久不見</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唱就人人都唱到<br />\n但邊有人可以唱到佢咁<br />\n聽過其他人唱到好平 訓著咁款"},{"pid":"1fac3488364d7bf020ed1c7cb22aa22d7976bef5","tid":285272,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:38:47.000Z","msg":"銀河唯一"},{"pid":"d4876af49f6c284d314de00fa667d1c71a4cfd50","tid":285272,"uid":39245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:40:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>超人的主題曲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有鋼鍊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ccfe8837fd08683233863fddf78d1f6c999101","tid":285272,"uid":61210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:40:50.000Z","msg":"爛"},{"pid":"2c905c0c6363827186feac128d1a2f3b8590b333","tid":285272,"uid":7062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:40:52.000Z","msg":"猜程尋"},{"pid":"1d341a44dbc07b296a0c24324384e8285e48100d","tid":285272,"uid":8940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我甚麼都沒有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce21b14c9c8bf59d733c1e0c49cb48837db9c1f","tid":285272,"uid":62551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:46:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實點定義為難唱先？<br />\n計音準嘅話<br />\n係咪代表好多人唔識唱歌？<br />\n定係佢地覺得難唱到eason咁有感情</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多巴打都話唱到eason既歌 但唱唔出佢既感情 或者咁形容： <br />\n 當你地指既感情 就係佢既音域 隻歌音域闊，而你無咁闊既音域 唱就變左唔岩feel/唔好聽，其實係因為音域窄先會有咁既錯覺</blockquote><br />\n仲有天生把聲呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小朋友音域都夠闊 把聲唔夠mature/唔夠磁性/timbre唔夠好 都唱唔出eason個feel</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEASON 聲樂8級 當然佢可能都有佢既天份,但係有天份唔練聲都係無用,張敬軒李克勤聲都靚<br />\n唔知EASON考聲樂8級之前係點既狀態 但係可以肯定佢有今日既聲線/用聲 都係靠練聲練返黎"},{"pid":"0c01f4cb3c92b824e145a779598b6c66645c634f","tid":285272,"uid":53364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:46:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我甚麼都沒有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\"